messages.content: Can you tell me how many days in April did we work?

Based on the provided context, the documents indicate the following workdays in April: 1. CPRPreviewSCA (6).pdf (Section 0): - Zenovii Dziuba worked on April 20 and April 21. - Ermilo Lopez worked on April 20. 2. CPRPreviewSCA (5).pdf (Section 0): - Zenovii Dziuba and Ermilo Lopez worked from April 11 to April 14. In total, the workdays in April for these employees were April 11, 12, 13, 14, 20, and 21. This totals to 6 workdays in April.
